            <h1 class="cs-title">Professional Web Design & Development <span class="cs-color">Services </span></h1>
            <h2>Custom Code - NO Page Builders Or Wordpress</h2>

            <p>
                At Oak Harbor Web Designs, we do things a little differently. Instead of using page builders or Wordpress, we hand write all the code for our sites from top to bottom. 
                This allows us to make very custom designs, have absolutely ZERO bloat or wasted code to slow us down, 
                they load instantly, score perfect marks on Google Page Speed Insights, are more secure and actually impossible to hack, 
                and we don't need to constantly update plugins or WordPress versions to prevent hacking.
            
            <h3>WHY IT MATTERS</h3>
           <ul>
    <li>Faster load times</li>
    <li>Better conversions</li>
    <li>Better performing ads</li>
    <li>More secure</li>
    <li>Better ranking on Google</li>
    <li>Boosts your Google Business Profile in the Maps Listings</li>
</ul>
            <h3>BETTER LOAD TIMES LEADS TO HIGHER CONVERSIONS</h3>
        <p>It's very competitive online, and you need every edge you can get to stand out and overtake your competition. 
    When everyone else is using a page builder and getting poor load times, you could be getting something different - 
    something custom coded and loading instantly. This is important because if your website takes 
    <strong>more than 3 seconds to load</strong>, <strong>you could lose up to 50% of your traffic</strong> 
    because they leave before the site can load. They just don't want to wait that long. 
    Our sites load so fast they don't have any chance to leave, 
    allowing us to capture more leads to the site than your old one did.</p>

    <h3>BETTER ADS PERFORMANCE</h3>
    <p>The faster your website loads, the better your conversions are for the ads to send them to. 
        And Google prefers websites that load fast. Faster loading websites actually have a lower 
        cost-per-click which can save you hundreds or more a month depending on how much you're spending on ads clicks.</p>
        
    
    <h3>CUSTOM CODED WEBSITES ARE MORE SECURE</h3>
    <p>WordPress and other builders have lots of vulnerabilities and points of entry into the site that can be compromised. Like with Wordpress, if you aren't constantly updating your plugins and WordPress 
        version then you are increasing the chances of getting hacked every day you don't. Hackers target WordPress more than any other platform because they are easier to get into 
        (especially if you aren't doing your updates!).
         With our custom code, we don't have any databases or server side requests being made that hackers can intercept and hijack to insert their own code to redirect a site to a spam site. 
        It's just static HTML and CSS files. There's nothing TO hack. We can leave our sites alone for 10 years and nothing will happen to them. They are as secure as you can get.</p>

        <h3>IMPROVE YOUR SEARCH RATING</h3>
        <p>Better load times can improve your ranking on Google in a number of ways. The most common way is by just being faster. If there are two similar sites with similar content and domain authority, Google has stated that the one with the better Page Speed Scores and Core Vitals will win.
            The other method is more indirect. When your site loads faster, more people reach it. And the more people you have going to your site can increase your ranking. And by 
            focusing on Google's Core Vitals Metrics we can create a better user experience on the site to keep them on the site with higher 
            session times and navigating the site with more clicks to other pages to learn more. With more traffic, higher session times, and better click through rates, we can improve our Google ranking by 
            showing Google we are solving the users search queries and are experts in our field that visitors find valuable with our carefully written and helpful content.</p>
    
            <h3>BOOST YOUR GOOGLE BUSINESS PROFILE</h3>

            <p>A faster loading website can also add extra boost to your Google Business Profile and help increase your visibility in Maps searches. Couple that with LOTS of 5 star reviews, 
                images, and a full 100% complete profile, you will start seeing more 
                leads coming from that profile than you had before. The more visible we can make your profile there, the more people that reach your site, 
                and that's more people that our site can convert into a lead.</p>
    
    </div>
